# telemetrix-lite (v0.1.0)

Teacher-friendly wrapper for Telemetrix adding polling-style helpers (digital/analog/debounce), sonar, I2C LCD,
and optional RFID helpers (PN532 UART; RC522 via Arduino sketch).

> Disclaimer: Independent educational wrapper; not affiliated with Telemetrix authors.

## Install
pip install .

## Quick start
from telemetrix_lite import TelemetrixSync
t = TelemetrixSync(); t.set_input(7, pullup=True); t.set_output(13)
while True:
    v = t.digital_read(7, default=1)
    if v == 0: t.digital_write(13,1)
    else: t.digital_write(13,0)
